@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### 1) LOGIN – get token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "example@example.com",
  "code": "supersecret123"
}

###
# After sending the LOGIN request above:
#  - copy the "token" value from the JSON response
#  - paste it EXACTLY into the Authorization header below
###

### 2) PROTECTED ENDPOINT – manual token paste
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/secret
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE


### 3) HEALTH THROUGH PROXY (sanity check)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health


### 4) LOGOUT – same token as above
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE